OL,7,FA mother from Stoke-on-Trent who
OL,8,Fkilled her young children in knife
OL,9,Fattacks described by a judge as
OL,10,F"almost too horrific to comprehend"
OL,11,Fhas been handed an indefinite hospital
OL,12,Forder.
OL,14,FA fact-finding trial in front of a
OL,15,Fjury at Nottingham Crown Court was
OL,16,Ftold how Veronique John, of Flax
OL,17,FStreet, Stoke, Staffordshire, killed
OL,18,Fher children at their home in June
OL,19,F2023 before going on to attack her
OL,20,Fhusband, Nathan.
