OL,7,FTelling Veronique John that the order
OL,8,Fmay mean she is never released from a
OL,9,Fsecure hospital, High Court Judge Mr
OL,10,FJustice Choudhury said the fatal
OL,11,Fattacks on her son Ethan, 11, and
OL,12,Fdaughter Elizabeth, 7, had been
OL,13,F"frenzied and heinous".
OL,15,FElizabeth was pronounced dead at her
OL,16,Fhome having suffered a fractured skull
OL,17,Fand knife wounds, while the 50-year-
OL,18,Fold's son, Ethan, suffered more than
OL,19,F20 sharp force injuries.
