OL,7,FJohn, who has been diagnosed with
OL,8,Fcomplex post-traumatic stress disorder
OL,9,Fas well as personality and depressive
OL,10,Fdisorders, was ruled unfit to enter a
OL,11,Fplea or take part in the trial.
OL,13,FPassing the hospital order, Mr Justice
OL,14,FChoudhury said the reason for the
OL,15,F"abominable savagery" shown in killing
OL,16,Fthe children appeared to be an attempt
OL,17,Fby John to "hurt" her husband because
OL,18,Fof fears he may take their children
OL,19,Faway.
