OL,7,FThe judge told John via a video-link
OL,8,Fto Rampton high security hospital:
OL,9,F"The facts of this case are almost too
OL,10,Fhorrific to comprehend."
OL,12,FThe wounds to John's son were "almost
OL,13,Fas if" she was trying to decapitate
OL,14,Fhim, the judge said.
OL,16,F"The injuries were no less horrifying
OL,17,Fin Elizabeth's case," the judge added.
