OL,7,FThe killing of the children appeared
OL,8,Fto have been an attempt to "hurt"
OL,9,Ftheir father and prevent him from
OL,10,Ftaking them away, Mr Justice Choudhury
OL,11,Ftold John.
OL,13,FJohn remained seated with her head
OL,14,Fbowed and wiped away tears as the
OL,15,Fjudge continued: "You claim that you
OL,16,Fare not a monster... but your acts
OL,17,Fwere either those of a monster or
OL,18,Fsomeone who has lost all capacity to
OL,19,Freason.
