OL,7,F"It's clear that by the time of the
OL,8,Ftrial you were not fit to plead. It
OL,9,Fhas been conclusively determined that
OL,10,Fyou did kill your own children and
OL,11,Fmake an attempt to kill Nathan."
OL,13,FA hospital order with a special
OL,14,Frestriction to protect the public was
OL,15,Fappropriate, the judge ruled, in light
OL,16,Fof the extreme and brutal violence
OL,17,Fused against two defenceless young
OL,18,Fchildren.
