OL,7,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,8,Fthe court by prosecutor Peter Grives-
OL,9,FSmith, Mr John, who was stabbed
OL,10,Fshortly after his children were
OL,11,Fattacked, said his wife had "viciously
OL,12,Fand brutally" taken their lives.
OL,14,FMr John said: "On June the 11th my
OL,15,Fwhole world was turned upside down. I
OL,16,Flost the two most important and
OL,17,Fprecious persons in my life at once."
