OL,7,FAfter hearing the evidence over five
OL,8,Fdays, the jurors deliberated for
OL,9,Faround 40 minutes before unanimously
OL,10,Fruling that John unlawfully inflicted
OL,11,Ffatal neck and head injuries on her
OL,12,Fchildren and stabbed her husband in
OL,13,Fthe stomach.
OL,15,FJohn, who was not in court to hear the
OL,16,Fjury's findings, now faces a mandatory
OL,17,Fhospital order admitting her to
OL,18,FNottinghamshire's Rampton high
OL,19,Fsecurity hospital.
