OL,8,Fprosecution, trial judge Mr Justice
OL,9,FChoudhury explained that the jurors'
OL,10,Ftask during the expected six-day trial
OL,11,Fwould be to find whether she did the
OL,12,Facts charged against her.
OL,14,FThe judge said: "This trial is
OL,15,Fslightly unusual ` the defendant has
OL,16,Fbeen found to be under a disability.
