OL,7,F"She is unable to participate in the
OL,8,Ftrial in any meaningful sense. Your
OL,9,Ftask is to decide whether the
OL,10,Fdefendant did the acts of unlawfully
OL,11,Finflicting injuries on and killing
OL,12,FEthan and Elizabeth which led to their
OL,13,Fdeaths, and unlawfully inflicting
OL,14,Finjuries to Mr John."
