OL,10,Findefinite hospital order.
OL,12,FDuring the trial the court was told
OL,13,FJohn, originally from the Caribbean
OL,14,Fisland of St Vincent, "erupted" into
OL,15,Fviolence at her home in Flax Street,
OL,16,FStoke, because she did not want her
OL,17,Fhusband, Nathan John, to have their
