OL,8,Fafter being arrested for assaulting
OL,9,Fher husband while suspecting him of
OL,10,Fhaving an affair, later stated in
OL,11,Finterview: "It's something I was
OL,12,Fthinking about for a long time ` just
OL,13,Fkill myself and the kids. Unless you
OL,14,Fguys are offering me the death penalty
OL,15,FI have nothing else to say.
OL,17,F"I did it because I love my children `
OL,18,Fto protect the children. If there's
OL,19,Fany possible way I could be put to
OL,20,Fdeath, I would like that. When I say
OL,21,Fthat I am not joking. I mean it 100%."
